node.text: Voodoo Ranger Country is everywhere. Everywhere there’s a fridge. Everywhere there’s a cooler. Everywhere there’s a tap. Everywhere people crave flavor. Flavor at a higher percentage than average. Are you living in Voodoo Ranger Country?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Voodoo Ranger on August 10, 2021.

node.text: It's not a real product, it's a real thought experiment: What would you want in your Rangerables box?

node.text: Grab a sixer and talk to Voodoo Ranger before all your hard decisions.

node.text: Sometimes I organize letters together in a strategic fashion on Twitter. Holler at your boy.

node.text: "Whoa is that a tall boy?" - Literally everyone who passes by me

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Voodoo Ranger on July 15, 2021 tagging @djtambe. May be an illustration.

node.text: Raise an IPA for 2X Ink Master champion, @DJtambe, on this killer Voodoo Ranger tattoo. Then, raise another IPA cause tomorrow’s Friday and you just about crushed another week.
Dial-up your internet and get V2K IPA. Download these sweet screensavers using the link in our bio.
